title: TW: Importing markdown files (from Roam)

Some notes on how I've been trying to pull in some of the pages from [[Roam]] via [[Markdown]] files

Install the Markdown plugin via the control panel UI

Edit the `$:/config/markdown/renderWikiTextPragma` tiddler and append `prettylink` to the end. This is so that wikilinks (`[[*]]`) are parsed. By default they are not.

